About Professor AI

Professor AI is an AI-powered personalized tutoring system that adapts to your learning style and academic background. The full version includes:

  • Personalized learning paths based on your goals
  • Interactive tutoring sessions with an AI tutor
  • Assessments to test your knowledge
  • Progress tracking and recommendations
